Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: OpenCV Import Errors
Solution: Reinstall OpenCV with proper dependencies

pip3 uninstall opencv-python
pip3 install opencv-python-headless
Issue: No Features Detected
Possible causes:

Image quality too low
Insufficient contrast
Wrong image format
Solution: Adjust detection thresholds and try different preprocessing techniques

Issue: EXIF Data Not Found
Explanation: Not all images contain EXIF metadata. Test images may lack this data.

Solution: Use real photographs from cameras or smartphones for EXIF analysis

Issue: Confidence Scores Always Low
Solution: Review your scoring algorithm and ensure all detection methods are properly implemented

